<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-67-0091 </DOCNO><TEXT>The principle is described of digital subtraction angiography and itsrole is assessed in the diagnosis of cerebrovascular disease. Its advantagesare pointed out, such as the intravenous route for the contrast mediumapplication, a lower radiation load to the patient, lower cost of examination.However, it only is complementary to conventional angiography and cannotreplace it. (L.O.). 1 fig., 3 refs.</TEXT></DOC>